 activity. ELIGIBILITY: Washington State residents who are originators of w
 orks of art and not current students\; open to artist teams.\n\nOrganisati
 on: Artist Trust\nLocation: Washington State\, United States\nAward: $2\,5
 00 unrestricted project grant per artist (awarded to 65 artists). No appli
 cation fee.\nDuration: Per project\n\nMore: https://artisttrust.org/grants
 /grants-for-artist-projects/
