DTSTAMP:20260601T084516Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260701
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260702
SUMMARY:Deadline: Light Work: Artist-in-Residence 2027
DESCRIPTION:One-month artist-in-residence programme at Light Work in Syracu
 se\, New York\, for artists working in photography or image-based media. R
